## ğŸ® BETA GAME COMPLETED
  âœ” "Gods of Olympus" Memory Game @started(25-06-09 22:45) @done(25-06-09 23:15) @lasted(30m)
    âœ” TypeScript interfaces and game types
    âœ” Zustand store for state management
    âœ” Greek gods data with 12 olympian deities
    âœ” Animated game components with Framer Motion
    âœ” Three difficulty levels (easy/medium/hard)
    âœ” Responsive design for all devices
    âœ” Victory and pause states
    âœ” Score tracking and statistics
    This is a memory game with 12 greek gods, its a matching game where you find
    a pair of the matching gods. There 3 difficulty levels, easy, medium and hard.
    The easy level has 12 cards, the medium level has 18 cards, and the hard level has 24 cards.
    The game is a timed game, you have 1 minute to find all the pairs. This
    could be applied to a english word and a differnt language word.

